query:
SELECT 
  ig.name,
  ig.slug,
  CASE 
    WHEN CHAR_LENGTH(COALESCE(ig.topThingsToDo, '')) > 100 THEN 'Complete'
    ELSE 'Incomplete'
  END as content_status
FROM island_guides ig
WHERE CHAR_LENGTH(COALESCE(ig.topThingsToDo, '')) <= 100
ORDER BY ig.name
